            <title>[SOLR-3082] If you use a lazy replication request handler, the commit listener will not be registered right away, and might miss tracking the last commit.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3082</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
